      <title>中国将进一步扩大油籽产量以减少进口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-to-further-expand-oilseed-production-to-reduce-imports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[明年，中国将在更多土地上种植油菜籽，并稳定大豆种植面积，扩大政策推动力，提高油籽收成，减少最大消费国对海外供应的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-to-further-expand-oilseed-production-to-reduce-imports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 06:16:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
