    <item>
      <title>中国滚雪球及其在今年股票抛售中的作用：问答</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-snowballs-and-their-role-in-this-year-s-stock-selloff-q-a</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国股市今年开局惨淡至少部分归咎于一种相对较新的金融衍生品“雪球”的影响。这些产品与指数挂钩，一个关键特征是，当指数跌破内置水平时，券商将出售其相关期货头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-23/china-snowballs-and-their-role-in-this-year-s-stock-selloff-q-a</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jan 2024 06:02:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
